The paper discusses the use of heuristic search techniques and domain-specific knowledge to solve optimization problems. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of logic programming and inductive logic programming also suggests that the paper could belong to the Data Mining (cs.DM) or Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. Finally, the focus on incorporating domain-specific knowledge suggests that the paper could also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
